[SN]TITLE[SN]
Blind man told to clear up dog mess in Hodnet

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A blind Shropshire man has been told he should clear up his dog's mess.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
8 December 2015 Last updated at 15:51 GMT
Hodnet Parish Council has suggested Brian Wood takes a companion with him, to help pick it up.
But Mr Wood said that would affect his independence.
